if you have flickering issues just do {FD_DEV_FEATURES : enable_tp_ubwc_flag_hint=1}

and if the audio clicks alot do {PLUSE_LATENCY_MSEC : 90}
(make sure your using pulse for that one)

if the game doesn't launch properly try heading to the appdata/roaming/sega and try editing the graphics.ini to have windowed=1 and if that doesn't work just delete it so the game remakes it

